frontmatter.title: Something went wrong installing the "sharp" module. Module did not self-register.
frontmatter.mdxPreview: I spent [more time than I'd care to admit](https://twitter.com/noahsark769/status/1231387394189824000?s=20) today trying to debug why my Github Actions workflow to automatically deploy new versions of noahgilmore.com on push to `master` was failing. The site is build on [Gatsby](https://www.gatsbyjs.org/), and the pipeline runs `gatsby build`, but I was running into the following error on every push...
